ebirth-lead-2024-game-award-nominations-3813944"><em>《Astro Bot》</em>和<em>《最终幻想 7 重生》</em>在 2024 年游戏奖提名中领跑</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/alien-rogue-incursion-is-being-released-next-month-3813971">下个月发布的《异形：盗贼入侵》</a>一文首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 Fatboy Slim 抨击绿洲重聚巡演的“病态”动态票价https://www.nme.com/news/music/fatboy-slim-hits-out-at-sick-dynamic-ticket-pricing-for-oasis-reunion-tour-3813973?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=fatboy-绿洲团聚之旅的生病动态门票定价苗条Liberty DunworthTue, 19 Nov 2024 12:00:12 +0000 Music NewsNewsBritpopElectronicIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3813973 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cook-Gallagher@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Fatboy Slim 和利亚姆·加拉格尔，2024 年。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cook-Gallagher@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cook-Gallagher@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cook-Gallagher@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cook-Gallagher@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cook-Gallagher@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cook-Gallagher@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “兜售者这么做已经够糟糕了，但真正的发起人和乐队这么做，就更恶心了”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fatboy-slim-hits-out-at-sick-dynamic-ticket-pricing-for-oasis-reunion-tour-3813973">Fatboy Slim 抨击 Oasis 重聚巡演动态票价“病态”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cook-Gallagher@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Fatboy Slim 和利亚姆·加拉格尔，2024 年。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cook-Gallagher@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cook-Gallagher@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cook-Gallagher@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cook-Gallagher@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cook-Gallagher@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Cook-Gallagher@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fatboy-slim">Fatboy Slim</a>对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">Oasis</a> 2025 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-uk-ireland-stadium-2025-liam-noel-gallagher-tickets-3787539">重聚巡演的</a>门票惨败进行了权衡，并将动态定价的使用称为“病态”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/oasis-reunion-line-up-band-members-guide-3788552">支持我：2025 年绿洲阵容中的所有球员</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">利亚姆·</a>加拉格尔 (Liam Gallagher) 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallagher">诺埃尔·加拉格尔 (Noel Gallagher)</a>今年早些时候宣布了这支标志性英伦流行乐队的重组，并确认明年夏天他们将一起进行自 2009 年以来的首次现场表演。</p><p>演出将从<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-uk-ireland-stadium-2025-liam-noel-gallagher-tickets-3787539">英国和爱尔兰的大型体育场演出</a>开始，然后从那里<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-add-extra-dates-to-north-american-2025-reunion-tour-due-to-phenomenal-demand-3799159">前往北美，</a>然后于九月下旬返回<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-wembley-stadium-extra-reunion-dates-tickets-invite-only-no-surge-pricing-3790552">伦敦温布利体育场进行两场额外的演出</a>。随后兄弟俩确认<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-add-more-dates-to-australia-2025-reunion-tour-3801693">将在澳大利亚墨尔本和悉尼演出</a>，并宣布<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-2025-south-american-reunion-tour-dates-the-brothers-are-coming-buy-tickets-3809661">16 年来首次南美演出。</a></p><p>然而，在英国和爱尔兰演出的门票上线后，乐队就成为了争议的焦点，因为一些歌迷在访问门票页面时 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-fans-react-to-ticketmasters-dynamic-pricing-3789361">发现，由于 Ticketmaster 的动态定价政策，价格大幅上涨</a>。</p><p>该票务平台于 2022 年推出的“峰时定价”计划，根据需求提高票价。 Ticketmaster 此前曾在其网站上澄清，门票是“市场定价”的，并且“可能根据需求随时增加或减少”。这类似于机票和酒店房间的销售方式。”</p><p>现在，Fatboy Slim 分享了他对所实施的票务策略的想法，并表达了他对现场表演使用动态定价的蔑视。 </p><figure id="attachment_3813978" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3813978" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3813978" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Norman-Cook@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Fatboy Slim 在 2024 年胜利节期间表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Norman-Cook@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Norman-Cook@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Norman-Cook@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Norman-Cook@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Norman-Cook@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Norman-Cook@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3813978" class="wp-caption-text"> Fatboy Slim 在 2024 年胜利音乐节期间表演。图片来源：Mark Holloway/Redferns/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> “我遇到的唯一问题是剥削球迷。这种动态定价，就是在敲诈粉丝。这就像拍卖门票，因为你知道他们做得很好，”他告诉<a href="https://www.thesun.co.uk/tvandshowbiz/31761961/fatboy-slim-slams-oasis-ticket-prices/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>太阳报的奇异</em>专栏</a>。 “兜售者这么做已经够糟糕了，但真正的发起人和乐队这么做，就更恶心了。”</p><p>他继续说道：“据我所知，在我任内从未发生过这种情况。我对订票有发言权，总的来说，便宜。我总是说，‘让我们有一个公平的价格’。门票价格这么贵。对于那些已经非常非常富有的人来说，这只是利润——对于乐队和发起人来说。</p><p> “我不明白你怎么能仅仅因为你知道你有一个每个人都想参加的演出就可以证明让它变得更加昂贵。”</p><p>值得注意的是，绿洲确实在9月份公开谈论了票务问题，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-band-say-they-at-no-time-had-any-awareness-that-dynamic-pricing-was-going-to-be-used-3790679">表示他们不知道票价会上涨如此之大。</a></p><p>更新中写道：“需要明确的是，绿洲将票务和定价的决定完全交给了他们的促销员和管理层，并且在任何时候都没有意识到将使用动态定价。”</p><p> “虽然主办方、Ticketmaster 和乐队管理层之前的会议达成了积极的门票销售策略，这对歌迷来说将是一次公平的体验，包括动态票务以帮助降低总体票价并减少兜售，但该计划的执行未能达到预期。所有相关方都尽最大努力提供尽可能最好的粉丝体验，但由于前所未有的需求，这是不可能实现的。” </p><figure id="attachment_3790242" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3790242" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3790242" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Noel-Liam-Gallagher.jpg" alt="绿洲乐队的利亚姆·加拉格尔和诺埃尔·加拉格尔" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Noel-Liam-Gallagher.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Noel-Liam-Gallagher-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Noel-Liam-Gallagher-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Noel-Liam-Gallagher-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Noel-Liam-Gallagher-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Noel-Liam-Gallagher-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3790242" class="wp-caption-text">绿洲乐队的利亚姆·加拉格尔和诺埃尔·加拉格尔。图片来源：Gie Knaeps/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>在接受<em>《太阳报》</em>采访时，Fatboy Slim（真名诺曼·库克）分享了他对<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coldplay-uk-tour-stadium-london-wembley-hull-music-venue-trust-tickets-3794308">酷玩乐队的支持，并发誓将在即将举行的巡演中帮助支持英国各地的草根音乐空间</a>。</p><p> “我真的很讨厌酷玩乐队。至少，我是这么做的，直到他们宣布他们的新竞技场巡演，并宣布他们将为整个巡演提供 10% 的票价，这将有助于维持较小的场馆的运营，”他说。</p><p> “这就是你应该拥有的动态定价。他们并不想赚很多钱，他们只是想生存。他们只是喜欢看摇滚乐……新乐队必须有地方来。”</p><p>在最初对 Oasis 门票的强烈反对之后，乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-are-preparing-to-cancel-more-than-50000-tickets-sold-via-secondary-ticket-sites-3807274">宣布他们将取消通过转售网站出售的数千张即将举行的英国 2025 年重聚巡演门票</a>。</p><p>关于动态定价的意见分歧也提交给了议会，据报道<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ticket-sellers-may-have-to-tell-fans-maximum-prices-after-oasis-dynamic-pricing-backlash-says-potential-new-law-3804848">可能会出台一项新法律，要求音乐和体育赛事在购票过程开始时告诉粉丝最高价格</a>。此举是在英国文化大臣<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/culture-secretary-lisa-nandy-condemns-oasis-dynamic-pricing-in-first-address-to-uk-music-industry-3802194">丽莎·南迪谴责动态定价</a>并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-ticket-sales-culture-secretary-lisa-nandy-calls-for-review-into-dynamic-pricing-and-secondary-ticket-sites-3789694">呼吁对该政策进行审查之后做出的。</a></p><p>大约在同一时间， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-hundreds-complain-to-asa-over-surge-ticket-pricing-3789875">该问题被提交给广告标准局</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-european-commission-reportedly-investigating-dynamic-pricing-amid-oasis-tickets-controversy-3790240">欧盟委员会</a>，并单独呼吁<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-ticket-sales-culture-secretary-lisa-nandy-calls-for-review-into-dynamic-pricing-and-secondary-ticket-sites-3789694">英国政府进行调查</a>。专家还建议，不警告 Oasis 粉丝动态定价<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/not-warning-oasis-fans-of-dynamic-pricing-may-be-law-breach-experts-say-3789896">可能违反消费者法</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3792129" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3792129" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3792129" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/oasis-which-ticketmaster@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/oasis-which-ticketmaster@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/oasis-which-ticketmaster@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/oasis-which-ticketmaster@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/oasis-which-ticketmaster@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/oasis-which-ticketmaster@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/oasis-which-ticketmaster@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3792129" class="wp-caption-text"> Ticketmaster 的 Oasis 页面。图片来源：马特·卡迪/盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>在遭到强烈反对后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-confirm-dynamic-pricing-will-not-be-applied-to-north-american-reunion-tour-dates-3798327">乐队后来确认动态定价结构不会应用于</a>他们的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-2025-reunion-tour-dates-in-north-america-and-mexico-buy-tickets-3798246">北美重聚巡演日期</a>。</p><p>至于宣布进一步亮相英国的希望， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-respond-to-glastonbury-2025-rumours-and-the-chances-of-other-festivals-3788269">Oasis 已经排除了在 2025 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节上进行头条表演的可能性</a>，并表示明年夏天他们不会出现在任何其他音乐节上。<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/could-oasis-return-to-knebworth-in-2026-3792709">利亚姆和诺埃尔也驳斥了 2026 年重返纳贝沃斯的传言</a>。</p><p>至于已经宣布的演出，已确认<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cage-the-elephant">Cage The Elephant</a>将在北美站担任开场支持，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-confirm-richard-ashcroft-as-special-guest-for-2025-uk-and-ireland-reunion-tour-3804758">前 Verve 主唱兼独奏者 Richart Ashcroft</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-cast-as-final-support-act-for-2025-uk-and-ireland-reunion-tour-3806934">Cast</a>将与曼彻斯特偶像一起参加英国和爱尔兰的演出。</p><p>至于 Fatboy Slim，这位艺术家将在 2024 年剩余时间内进行更多现场表演，包括在英国和美国的演出。他还已确认参加 2025 年夏季的音乐节，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/latitude-festival-announces-headliners-for-2025-buy-tickets-3806899">Latitude</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kendal-calling-2024-line-up-the-prodigy-courteeners-fatboy-slim-kaiser-chiefs-and-more-announced-buy-tickets-3808588">Kendal Calling</a>的头条新闻。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fatboy-slim-hits-out-at-sick-dynamic-ticket-pricing-for-oasis-reunion-tour-3813973">Fatboy Slim 抨击 Oasis 重聚巡演动态票价“病态”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
